Rb8 $5 $16) 15. Bxa8 ({Less advisable is} 15. exf4 c6 $16) 15... Bxh2+ $2 (
15... Be5 $142 16. Bd5+ Kh8 $16) 16. Kxh2 $18 Qh4+ (16... c6 17. Kg1 Qe5 $18)
17. Kg1 c6 18. Rfd1 f4 (18... Qf6 {doesn't change the outcome of the game} 19.
