b4 axb4 19. Rxa8 Qxa8 20. Ra1 {White threatens to win material: Ra1xa8} (20.
cxb4 f5 21. Nc7 Bf7 22. Qxf5 Qc8 23. Qxc8 Rxc8 $16) 20... Qb8 (20... Qb7 21.
Ra6 Ne7 22. Ncxb4 $16 (22. Rxd6 $6 Bf7 23. Qh3 bxc3 $11)) 21. cxb4 (21. Ncxb4
Bf7 22. Qf5 Nxb4 23. cxb4 Re8 $16) 21... Bf7 (21... f5 22. Bc4 Kh8 23. b5 $14)
22. Qg4 (22. Qf5 Qc8 23. Nxf6+ Bxf6 24. Qxf6 Nd4 25. Nxd4 Qc3 $18) 22... Qd8 (
22... f5 23. Nf6+ Kh8 24. Qxf5 $14) 23. b5 Ne7 (23... f5 $142 24. Qxf5 Bxd5 $16
) 24. b6 $4 {gives the opponent counterplay} (24. Nxf6+ $142 {White has a
